                    <a href="#" class="mn-has-sub">LANGUAGE <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i></a>
                    <ul class="mn-sub">
                        <li><a href="/Product/Mobile?lang=0">KOREA</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/Product/Mobile?lang=1">ENGLISH</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>


<!-- 1 -->
<div class="fullwidth-slider owl-carousel">
    <section class="page-section bg-scroll bg-color-white">
        <div class="container relative">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7 animate-init" data-anim-type="fade-in-right-big" data-anim-delay="100">
                    <!-- Image -->
                    <div class="work-full-media mt-0 align-center">
                        <img src="~/Lib/GOQUAL/images/product/mobile/product_mobile_1.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-1 pt-20 pt-sm-0 animate-init" data-anim-type="fade-in-left-big" data-anim-delay="100">
                    <!-- About Project -->
                    <div class="text">
                        @if (Model.Lang == 1)
                        {
                            <h3><span class="goqual_color">B</span>lueswitch</h3>
                            <h3>Brighten world again</h3>
                            <div class="section-heading align-left mb-20 mb-xxs-10 goqual_company_text">
                                In 1880 Thomas Edison invented the light bulb.
                                Since then, we can't imagine our life without light.
                                Thanks to the switch se have learned how to control light easily.
                                But since those 100 years the light switch hasn't been changed at all.
                                So, today we have developed for you smart and innovative switch.
                                It will make your world brighter.
                            </div>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <h3><span class="goqual_color">B</span>lueswitch</h3>
                            <h3>새롭게 세상을 밝힌다.</h3>
                            <div class="section-heading align-left mb-20 mb-xxs-10 goqual_company_text">
                                1880년 에디슨이 전구를 발명함으로써 인간은 언제든 빛을 가질 수 있었습니다.
                                그 빛을 쉽게 켜고 끄는 스위치도 함께 발명되었죠.
                                하지만 100년이 넘는 시간동안 스위치는 처음과 별반 다를게 없습니다.
                                우리는 오늘 새롭게 세상을 밝히게 될 멋진 스위치를 개발하였습니다.
                                더 밝은 세상, 더 나은 세상을 위하여.
                            </div>
                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

